1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Madam Liu didn't bleed — she burst into black smoke.
Everyone saw it. Everyone kept quiet. That's how a demon dies.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
I need time — time to figure out what's inside this body.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:19,000
Myriad-Demon Bloodline System. Level 1.
Warning: if your demon awakening tops 50%, you lose your mind — for good.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Refining Madam Liu's leftover demon blood... Done. EXP +10.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Jade Demon Rank unlocked. Body +100%, Speed +80%, Senses +50%.
New skill: Demonic Aura.

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:31,000
Okay, that's just ridiculous.

7
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Demonic Aura — on.

8
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:42,000
That black cat out back? Lowest-tier spirit. The woman in the west wing — human.

9
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Three of them under the locust tree... and something big at the bottom of that well.

10
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,500
The cold palace is a hunting ground. The fallen concubines? They're the prey.

11
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,000
No wonder they keep "dying of illness" and vanishing.

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,500
My lady... you look amazing today.

13
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:52,000
Get some sleep tonight. Whatever you hear — don't come out.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,000
My lady, what are you going to do?

15
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,000
Hunt demons.
